import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-restaurant-information', templateUrl: './restaurant-information.component.html', styleUrls: ['./restaurant-information.component.css'] }) export class RestaurantInformationComponent { constructor(private router: Router) { } navigateTo(newPage: number) { localStorage.setItem("page", newPage.toString()) this.router.navigate(["guest"]) } }
